data.description:
If you're looking for a home close to downtown Winnsboro amenities, this is it! Just a block north of downtown, this Winnsboro ISD home offers convenience and comfort. This home features 3 beds, 2 baths, 1636 Sq Ft, a 2 car garage, and an open floor plan. The kitchen has been updated with new granite counter tops, a new sink and faucet, and more. The HVAC, roof, electrical, and plumbing have also been updated and serviced with the current ownership. Hardwood floors run through the home, as well as built-in wood cabinetry in the kitchen and bathrooms. Sit outside on the covered front porch with a cup of coffee to watch the sunrise and sunset! 

Seller is motivated and willing to pay for Home Warranty Plan, and a portion of closing costs or a 2-1 rate buy-down. Furniture and appliances are negotiable as well.
